default7.default default defaultConclusiondefault&#xa0;
default7.1 There is never a good time for something like this to happen but Gatwick Airport recognises that Christmas Eve is probably the worst with so many passengers tr
defaultavelling to be with their families over the festive period.
default7.2 Gatwick Airport
default 
defaultwill learn the lessons, make any additional
default 
defaultinvestment required
default 
defaultand continue
default 
defaultto do everything it can to give its customers the quality of service they should expect.
default7.3 Gatwic
defaultk Airport's Chief Executive extends a sincere apology to those whose travel plans were disrupted.
